pros:
Some of the best reasons to work for IBM:
 - multinational company;
 - the chance to work in a multicultural environment;
 - the chance to work with and meet very well experienced coworkers;
 - it has everything you need to build your IT career; It covers every aspect, form hardware to services...!

Work with  different  technologies (mature ones  and cutting edge); 
really  good work/life balance; 
IBM reputation  still matters for carrer development

cons:
A very huge company;
very slow changes but management always tries to transform something;
salary increasing is very depends on particular first line manager;
no any other valuble benefits
